	<text>The Slug vessel has been destroyed. Unfortunately the wreckage damages the landscape, but none of the animals are hit. While you are scrapping the wreckage you notice several Slugs are still on the ground tormenting the equinoids.</text>
	<autoReward level="HIGH">standard</autoReward>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Continue...</text>
		<event>
			<text>Before you can do anything, the grey cloud suddenly grows larger and conceals the Slugs in a curtain of grey. You hear a blood curdling scream and suddenly the cloud dissipates, leaving nothing but puddle of lacerated flesh and blood. "We warned them not to disturb the equinoids... Some people simply do not listen..."</text>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Continue...</text>
				<event>
					<text>You watch as the Story Teller floats back to his ship, where it waits for you. "It is unusual that you chose to assist us. It is true you found this place because of our vessel, correct? Then take it. We have no need for it any more."</text>
					<unlockCustomShip silent="false">PLAYER_SHIP_CLAN</unlockCustomShip>
					<autoReward level="HIGH">standard</autoReward>
					<choice hidden="true">
						<text>Accept the ship and leave.</text>
						<event>
							<text>"Goodbye, friend. We will make sure your story does not go untold..."</text>
						</event>
					</choice>
					<choice hidden="true" req="LIST_CREW_JERRY">
						<text>(Jerry) "I think I'm the boy in your story..."</text>
						<event>
							<text>The Story Teller drifts over to Jerry, and slowly begins to condense into the form of a crimson Engi. "Our friend. It has been so long since we have seen you... How have the stars aligned to grant us this reunion? We can still see the innocence in your eyes. We apologize for our ramblings. How we wish we could join you, but we cannot. What we can offer is a gift. We wish you the best of journeys, Jerry, and your friends. Now this story can finally have a happy ending..."</text>
							<crewMember amount="1" combat="2" class="ponyc"/>
							<unlockCustomShip silent="false">PLAYER_SHIP_PONY_2</unlockCustomShip>
						</event>
					</choice>
					<choice hidden="true">
						<text>Offer to take the Story Teller with you.</text>
						<event>
							<text>"We're afraid we must never leave this place. A good guardian would never leave behind that which they protect. You have no need for us regardless. We are not fighters. Do not worry, we will make sure your story does not go untold..."</text>
						</event>
					</choice>
				</event>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
</event>

<ship name="SHIP_SALT_ABANDONED" auto_blueprint="MU_SALT_CRUISER">
