<event name="NEBULA_CLAN_PHEROMONES" unique="true">
	<text>You've seen a lot of things in your travels, but you don't think you've ever seen the wastes of half a Mantis fleet lying before a Guild megastructure. A massive mechanic arm appears to be collecting the wrecks one by one and moving them towards a small docking bay.</text>
