			<text>You pilot towards the structure and enter through a hangar door, where you're greeted by a Clansman. "Oh god, you aren't here to ssshut usss down, are you?"</text>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>I don't think so.</text>
				<event>
					<text>"Oh thank god. Wait, ssso why are you here? Have you come to watch my operation? Thisss here isss a pheromone extraction plant. The pheromone bussinesss isss booming, and we want to get a firm grip on it before thossse Free Mantiss bastardsss monopolizzze the whole thing."</text>
					<choice>
