									<text>"Oh! For once, Federation have good idea. Why not thinking that, instead of killing Slug... You make good point. I pay you for having smart brain and helping me."</text>
									<autoReward level="MED">standard</autoReward>
								</event>
							</choice>
						</event>
					</choice>
					<choice hidden="true">
						<text>But don't you all hate each other?</text>
						<event>
							<text>"Yes, of course! Slug greedy, Rockman slow, dumb. Leech smelly, reminding me of old corpse as I wishing they were. Mantis not standing these, but Hive say alliance good for keeping Slug out of Mantis territory."</text>
							<choice hidden="true">
								<text>Wouldn't an alliance mean more Slugs are in Mantis Territory?</text>
								<event>
									<text>"If it were dumb Federation, yes! But we smarter, alliance not grant permit for other race in other territory. Coalition territory shared, all others independent. Vital for Coalition survival. Making sense to you?"</text>
									<choice hidden="true">
										<text>Yes of course.</text>
										<event>
											<text>"Good. Now stop talking me, very boring and tiresome."</text>
										</event>
									</choice>
									<choice hidden="true">
										<text>No, I'm still confused.</text>
										<event>
											<text>"Gah, very annoying. Ask too many question, not understand anything! Federation captain miniscule intelligence, I will kill!"</text>
											<ship hostile="true"/>
											<choice hidden="true">
												<text>Continue...</text>
												<event load="COMBAT_CHECK"/>
											</choice>
										</event>
									</choice>
								</event>
							</choice>
						</event>
					</choice>
					<choice hidden="true">
						<text>I see. This definitely answers my question.</text>
						<event>
							<text>"Good. Now stop talking me, very boring and tiresome."</text>
						</event>
					</choice>
				</event>
			</choice>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>I feel you man. Slugs suck.</text>
				<event>
					<text>"Yes yes, we agree on this. Glad see other rational thinking man in space, even if smelly Fed! We Slug hater must band together, and fight off smelly Slug." The Suzerain is so pleased with you agreeing with him he even offers to patch up some of your hull damage.</text>
