				<event/>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Ignore the Suzerains.</text>
		<event>
			<text>You don't know why the Hive has one of its most feared warriors so far out in Slug space, but it's probably not good.</text>
