</event>
<textList name="NEBULA_SHELL_CLAN_FIGHT">
	<text>You wouldn't be one to expect Shells to be so hostile, but apparently the ongoings of the Guild have really agitated the nearby ship, because they're already attacking!</text>
	<text>Shells are normally very appreciative of science, but the ship here appears to have abandoned all reason and is attacking straight on. The Guild probably has something to do with this rash behavior, but it's too late to diagnose it now!</text>
	<text>"You must run! My crew, thhhey have caught a rare case of space rabies from an Equinoid we recovered during a raid on a Guild stati-" The Shell is cut off as he is murdered by one of his friends, who moves to take control of the ship and attack.</text>
</textList>


