<textList name="NEBULA_KNIGHT_FIGHT">
	<text>"Thessse nebulasss aren't for the Federation to be sssnooping around in! Get lossssst."</text>
	<text>The Knights of Nights sure are determined not to let anyone interfere with the festival. Despite you not even being able to participate, the mere suggestion you might be working with Slocknog is enough to drive the ship nearby to murder.</text>
	<text>A Knight ship jumps in, weapons blazing. It's not usual for Slugs to attack in such a blunt manner, but judging from the strange flight patterns of the ship, they're likely drunk. Let's hope that plays in your favor.</text>
	<text>It appears a Knight vessel is waiting for you here. "I made a bet that I would be the one to kill you! Now ssssit ssstill and let me blow you up."</text>
	<text>A Knight vessel appears to just have finished salvaging the remains of a small Slug interceptor, but as soon as you enter they decide to pick you off next!</text>
